    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can use a Magic action transform into an avatar of your divine might. You remain in your avatar form for 1 minute, until you are incapacitated, or until you use a Bonus Action to return to your normal form. While the transformation lasts, you gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li>If your size was originally Medium or Small, your size increases to Large.</li><li>You gain temporary Hit Points equal to twice your level.</li><li>You gain a Fly Speed equal to your Speed.</li></ul><p>Choose either Necrotic or Radiant. You gain Resistance to the chosen damage type. In addition, your Melee weapon attacks and Unarmed Strikes deal an extra [[/r 1d6]] damage of the chosen type. Once you use this boon, you can't do so again until you finish a Long Rest.</p>",
